      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Manychat is a chat marketing automation platform. Plain and simple, it lets you build automated conversation flows that run inside Instagram DMs, WhatsApp, Facebook Messenger, Telegram, and — more recently — TikTok. Think of it as a tireless assistant that replies to DMs, qualifies leads, delivers lead magnets, segments audiences, and closes sales while you sleep.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
