            "text": "Meta Business Partner",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and a TikTok Marketing Partner, which means these integrations are deep and officially supported — not fragile workarounds that break every time the API changes.",
