      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Manychat ships updates frequently. Here are the standout additions and improvements that make the platform feel genuinely next-level right now.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. TikTok Integration",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/manychat-use-cases"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is the headline addition for 2025. You can now trigger Manychat automations directly from TikTok comments and DMs. Imagine someone comments \"info\" on your viral TikTok — Manychat catches that keyword and slides into their DMs automatically with your sales message, a discount code, or a free resource. For creators who live on TikTok, this is transformative. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Read our TikTok automation use cases",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " for concrete examples.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. WhatsApp Business API Access",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "WhatsApp is no longer a second-class citizen. Manychat now offers native WhatsApp automation through the official Business API, with support for template messages, interactive buttons, and catalog integrations. The pricing for WhatsApp includes per-conversation fees set by Meta, but Manychat handles all the technical plumbing for you. If your audience is international — especially in Latin America, Europe, or India — WhatsApp automation is non-negotiable.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. AI-Powered Keyword & Intent Detection",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Old-school chatbots relied on rigid keyword matching. Type \"price\" and you get the price. Type \"how much\" and you get… nothing. Manychat's newer AI features use natural language understanding so the bot catches intent even when people phrase things differently. Fewer dead ends, more conversions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Improved Growth Tools & Comment Automation",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The comment automation engine got a significant upgrade. You can now set different auto-replies based on specific keywords found in comments, track which posts generate the most DM conversations, and even trigger different flows depending on whether someone is a new follower or a returning contact. The 60+ ready-made templates in the Free plan make setup remarkably fast.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. Multi-Channel Flows",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-manychat"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One of Manychat's strongest moves: you can now build a single automation that spans multiple channels. Start a conversation on Instagram, then follow up via WhatsApp or SMS if the contact doesn't finish the flow. Cross-channel persistence means fewer lost leads. For a deep dive into workflow building, check out our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step Manychat tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "6. Expanded Integration Ecosystem",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l5",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-n8n"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Manychat plays nicely with Zapier, Make (formerly Integromat), Google Sheets, HubSpot, Stripe, and dozens more. If you want to send every new lead straight into your CRM or trigger an email sequence after a conversation, the plumbing is already there. And if you are into advanced automation, you can even ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
