      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "E-commerce brands",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that sell through Instagram shops or WhatsApp catalogs. Automate product inquiries, send cart abandonment reminders inside DMs, and share checkout links without lifting a finger. If you run a Shopify store, the Stripe integration lets you process payments directly inside the chat.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Content creators and influencers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " who get buried in DMs after every post or Reel. Instead of ignoring 90% of messages, set up a flow that delivers your freebie, answers FAQs, and segments followers by interest.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Coaches, consultants, and course sellers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " who use social media as a top-of-funnel channel. Someone comments \"interested\" on your post → Manychat DMs them → qualifies their budget and readiness → books them into your calendar. Zero manual effort.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Agencies",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " managing multiple clients. Manychat's Pro plan supports multiple Instagram accounts, and the workspace structure makes client management clean. Agencies on PartnerStack can even resell Manychat and earn recurring commissions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Small businesses",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " on a tight budget. The Free plan genuinely works: 25 active contacts per month, two connected channels (pick from Instagram, TikTok, Messenger, or Telegram), and up to four active automations. For a local restaurant, a boutique fitness studio, or a freelance photographer, that is enough to handle the majority of incoming DM traffic without paying a cent.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
