        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For many small businesses, the jump from Free to the $15/month Pro plan is the only upgrade they will ever need. That $15 gets you unlimited channels, 500 contacts, and every automation feature — which is genuinely generous compared to alternatives that gate basic functionality behind $50+ plans.",
