            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start with comment automation, not DM blasts.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Comment-triggered flows feel natural to the user — they asked for something and got a response. Unsolicited DMs feel spammy. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Read our full tips guide",
