        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The fact that it holds official partnerships with both Meta and TikTok tells you something — these platforms trust Manychat with their APIs, which means your automations are stable and future-proof.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "And the numbers back it up: over one million businesses and creators use Manychat, and it holds a strong rating on G2. That is not hype; that is a track record.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
