        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Manychat really free?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. The Free plan includes 25 active contacts per month, two connected channels, and up to four active automations. No credit card needed. It is a genuine free tier, not a teaser that locks away essentials.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does Manychat work with WhatsApp Business?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "It does. Manychat integrates with the official WhatsApp Business API, supporting template messages, interactive buttons, and catalog sharing. Keep in mind that Meta charges per-conversation fees on top of your Manychat subscription.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I use Manychat for TikTok?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Manychat is an official TikTok Marketing Partner. You can trigger automations from TikTok comments and DMs, making it one of the few platforms that offer native TikTok chat automation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How many automations can I build?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Free plan allows up to four active automations. The Pro plan removes this limit entirely — build as many flows as your strategy requires.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What happens if I exceed my contact limit?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Manychat notifies you when you are approaching your cap. You can either upgrade to the next tier or let new contacts queue until the next billing cycle resets your count.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
